name: #07 - Transcend
description:
(Unmute Sound for Optimal Experience)

Fragment 07 - Transcend
(From the BINARY EMOTIONS series)

"The vision of the eye is limited but the vision of the heart transcends all barriers of time and space. The need is not to amputate the ego but to Transcend it."

TRANSCEND: It's dedicated to only the extent that someone is living out this self-transcendence of human existence. Is he truly human or does he become his true self? He becomes so, not by concerning himself with his self-actualization, but by forgetting himself and giving himself, overlooking himself, and focusing outward.
